title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 19 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Oct 19 2022
description:
Desperate Biden releases more oil ahead of election. Governor DeSantis rebuilds Sanibel Island Causeway in record time, although Dems said he couldn't. GOP congressional candidate in Florida, Anna Paulina Luna, joins Clay and Buck to discuss the Democrats throwing the kitchen sink at her. Young GOP candidates are rising stars. Biden on oil prices.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
